psalm.text:
[[Ps 2,7b]]The LORD said to me, "You are my Son;
[[Ps 2,7c]]this day I have begotten you."
[[Ps 2,8]]"Ask of me and I will give you the nations for an inheritance 
and the ends of the earth for your possession.

[[Ps 2,10]]And now, O kings, give heed; 
take warning, you rulers of the earth.
[[Ps 2,11]]Serve the LORD with fear, and rejoice before him; 
with trembling rejoice.

[[Ps 2,12a]]
